{"tid":1119853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果華仔選特首， 連登仔會唔會支持佢","createTime":"2019-04-22T08:28:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T10:41:59.000Z","uid":229185,"like":4,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4822c777003677a344c1c6c748eee9916232594a","tid":1119853,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rKH7rqA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrKH7rqA.jpg&h=c39632e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「我不是一個政治人物，我只是一個來打破體制的普通人。」在周日（21日）烏克蘭總統次輪選舉大敗現任總統波羅申科（Petro Poroshenko）的喜劇演員澤倫斯基（Volodymyr Zelensky）曾如此描述自己&mdash;&mdash;據票站調查結果顯示，澤倫斯基以73%的絕對優勢擊敗波羅申科，將出任下屆烏克蘭總統。<br />\n<br />\n沒有任何政治經驗的澤倫斯基，之所以能在年初「突然參選」以來，一舉擊敗烏克蘭的所有傳統政治勢力，全因民眾對國家貪污、財閥壟斷等各項積弊已到了忍無可忍的地步。<br />\n<br />\n有澤倫斯基的支持者就表示：「澤倫斯基有90%會是個災難，不過我還是會投票給他，因為我100%知道現任總統是個災難，我當然要為這10%的變革機會去博一博。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不了"},{"pid":"8dfd0e8aad40c55e41dd1d4c293a0bf072c53d7c","tid":1119853,"uid":172009,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:30:42.000Z","msg":"填海華 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc784abd61cf68fadccb69f45da8a53d3c453d08","tid":1119853,"uid":36296,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:31:46.000Z","msg":"黃子華就支持"},{"pid":"6663585028ff82daccae6c89dcbc31d8e032e224","tid":1119853,"uid":87339,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:34:17.000Z","msg":"明日大嶼"},{"pid":"2a4f2271229c95edfa9adbda0bf186d36ca0413b","tid":1119853,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:39:59.000Z","msg":"填海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n瞞婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a8397c5bba58a1eca5654b2df7b004b9dad2f5","tid":1119853,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:41:11.000Z","msg":"支持何韻詩好過"},{"pid":"517912fb9c7cbceeeef8193a9393cc34e9198102","tid":1119853,"uid":52595,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:42:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e723d44cb26db8e40aa6ebbddfe1c1bfd4e70a7","tid":1119853,"uid":140769,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:52:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e362d07718af7c508810252944c7291da8d0ec3f","tid":1119853,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e723d44cb26db8e40aa6ebbddfe1c1bfd4e70a7","tid":1119853,"uid":140769,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f8a8397c5bba58a1eca5654b2df7b004b9dad2f5","tid":1119853,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:41:11.000Z","msg":"支持何韻詩好過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:52:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48214267d8c1901a27c27aff54b17edd1696dc4e","tid":1119853,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:07:04.000Z","msg":"Sammi選就支持喇 <br />\n連登仔見人咁撚慘就覺得人又靚又性 <br />\n又罵尻人00後 <br />\n佢選實政治正確 又企到道德高地"},{"pid":"0cb704aadb2566ac90fe6b4f64a4f0bfaa2408d0","tid":1119853,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T10:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}